WEBVTT

00:00.368 --> 00:01.701
Previously on Beyond...

00:01.736 --> 00:03.653
You have no idea why
I called you up here today.

00:03.705 --> 00:05.004
Shoemacher.

00:08.827 --> 00:10.743
I keep having visions,

00:10.745 --> 00:12.795
and I don't know what they mean.

00:14.000 --> 00:20.074
