00:21.005 --> 00:22.004
Hey, taxi!

00:22.057 --> 00:24.674
Fort Reed, Kansas.

00:24.726 --> 00:26.092
You'll never guess who I saw yesterday.

00:26.094 --> 00:27.093
Charlie?

00:29.002 --> 00:32.709
- Sync and corrections by ByDem -
